Oh my God. Those are
so much better than mine.

1531
01:21:19,840 --> 01:21:22,530
Don't... touch me!

1532
01:21:22,710 --> 01:21:25,140
I got out of that car
the same way I got in it...

1533
01:21:25,310 --> 01:21:28,970
without you.
Now where is she?

1534
01:21:35,550 --> 01:21:37,240
You here with the bride
or the groom?

1535
01:21:37,410 --> 01:21:39,380
I'm here with my mother.

1536
01:21:45,390 --> 01:21:46,880
She looked a lot older. L...

