01:21:50,290 --> 01:21:52,120
Well, look
what we have here.

1538
01:21:52,300 --> 01:21:54,290
Oh my God.

1539
01:21:55,370 --> 01:21:57,200
You look beautiful.
Oh my God.

1540
01:21:57,370 --> 01:21:59,120
