1546
01:22:10,870 --> 01:22:14,200
Knock knock.
Look at you!

1547
01:22:14,380 --> 01:22:17,880
And so is your
mother-in-law.

1548
01:22:18,050 --> 01:22:20,140
Mm. Mm-mm-mm.

1549
01:22:21,150 --> 01:22:22,970
All right.
Everybody out.

1550
01:22:23,150 --> 01:22:25,310
Out.
Give the bride a moment.

1551
01:22:28,220 --> 01:22:30,980
- No way.
- What?

1552
01:22:36,460 --> 01:22:37,950
What is that?

1553
01:22:38,120 --> 01:22:40,550
- What?
- Where's your bridesmaid's dress?

1554
01:22:40,730 --> 01:22:42,860
I gave it
to Ruby's daughter.

1555
01:22:43,030 --> 01:22:44,680
She works at Hooters.
She was thrilled.

1556
01:22:44,860 --> 01:22:46,920
