1557
01:22:48,510 --> 01:22:49,840
Rude.

1558
01:22:51,640 --> 01:22:53,430
Take off that
white dress right now

1559
01:22:53,610 --> 01:22:56,700
or I'll take it off
for you.

1560
01:22:56,860 --> 01:22:58,920
Don't you tell me
what to do!

1561
01:22:59,100 --> 01:23:01,730
You did not
just poke me!

1562
01:23:01,900 --> 01:23:04,420
Don't you touch me,
you two-bit tramp!

1563
01:23:06,500 --> 01:23:08,230
Oh my God!
Viola, I'm so sorry.

1564
01:23:08,400 --> 01:23:10,760
I didn't mean to...

1565
01:23:10,930 --> 01:23:12,900
You don't go and slap somebody
then apologize.

1566
01:23:13,080 --> 01:23:14,640
Get some backbone!

1567
01:23:20,850 --> 01:23:22,770
God! This is crazy!

1568
01:23:22,950 --> 01:23:24,380
Why don't you just
face it?

1569
01:23:24,550 --> 01:23:26,710
I'm marrying Kevin today and there's
nothing you can do about it.

1570
01:23:26,890 --> 01:23:29,710
You face it! You'll never be
good enough for him!

1571
01:23:29,880 --> 01:23:32,240
Didn't stop you
from marrying my son.

1572
01:23:32,420 --> 01:23:35,710
- Oh God, no.
- Well, look at you.

1573
01:23:35,880 --> 01:23:37,580
All in white.

1574
01:23:37,750 --> 01:23:40,050
You are so predictable.

1575
01:23:40,230 --> 01:23:42,760
Gertrude.
I didn't know you were coming.

1576
01:23:42,930 --> 01:23:43,880
You didn't?

1577
01:23:44,060 --> 01:23:46,790
Wonder why.
I know.

1578
01:23:46,960 --> 01:23:49,520
You didn't send me
an invitation!

1579
01:23:49,700 --> 01:23:50,860
I thought you
were dead.

1580
01:23:51,030 --> 01:23:52,750
But evil doesn't die
so easily.

1581
01:23:52,930 --> 01:23:55,590
I heard you got sacked
and thrown into a loony bin.

1582
01:23:55,760 --> 01:23:57,800
- My congratulations.

1583
01:23:57,970 --> 01:23:59,530
Oh my God.

1584
01:23:59,710 --> 01:24:01,400
Oh my God!

1585
01:24:01,570 --> 01:24:03,500
These hors d'oeuvres
taste like old socks.

1586
01:24:05,680 --> 01:24:07,330
Now, I want to get

1587
01:24:07,500 --> 01:24:09,360
