01:26:55,130 --> 01:26:57,120
Charlie, what's wrong?

1637
01:26:59,530 --> 01:27:01,060
What is it?

1638
01:27:01,240 --> 01:27:02,560
Are you nervous?

1639
01:27:02,730 --> 01:27:04,530
Hey.

1640
01:27:06,740 --> 01:27:08,630
- Kevin, I need...
- Charlie,

1641
01:27:08,800 --> 01:27:10,560
I need to talk to you.

1642
01:27:10,740 --> 01:27:13,460
- Viola, stop it!
- It's the flower girls.

1643
01:27:13,630 --> 01:27:16,390
- They're drunk again.
- What?

1644
01:27:16,570 --> 01:27:17,980
Yeah, in the toilet.

1645
01:27:18,150 --> 01:27:19,540
Not now, Viola, okay?

1646
01:27:19,710 --> 01:27:21,130
It's really important.

1647
01:27:21,310 --> 01:27:23,470
Just give us a minute.
She'll be right there.

1648
01:27:25,340 --> 01:27:27,040
Please?

1649
01:27:27,220 --> 01:27:29,210
Charlie, what is it?

1650
01:27:33,550 --> 01:27:35,480
I'll be right back.

1651
01:27:40,690 --> 01:27:42,680
What do you want, Viola?

1652
01:27:44,360 --> 01:27:46,620
I don't want you
to walk out on this wedding.

1653
01:27:46,800 --> 01:27:48,100
You don't?

1654
01:27:48,270 --> 01:27:50,290
No, I don't.

1655
01:27:50,460 --> 01:27:52,820
What, am I supposed to believe
that you've had some epiphany?

1656
01:27:53,000 --> 01:27:55,300
That all of the sudden,
everything is going to be different?

1657
01:27:55,470 --> 01:27:57,190
It's never been
about you, Charlie.

1658
01:27:57,370 --> 01:27:59,000
It's me.

1659
01:27:59,170 --> 01:28:00,820
I've been so afraid
of losing him.

1660
01:28:01,000 --> 01:28:03,060
He's the only family
I've got.

1661
01:28:03,230 --> 01:28:07,440
This is my chance
for a family, too.

1662
01:28:07,620 --> 01:28:09,340
- And I'm scared.

1663
01:28:09,510 --> 01:28:11,610
Don't blow your chance
for happiness.

1664
01:28:11,780 --> 01:28:13,400
You've never needed
my approval.

1665
01:28:13,580 --> 01:28:15,850
He's loved you
from the very beginning.

1666
01:28:17,010 --> 01:28:19,700
And I promise I will
get out of the way

1667
01:28:19,880 --> 01:28:21,080
and let the two of you
be happy.

1668
01:28:21,250 --> 01:28:23,140
That's not what I want.

1669
01:28:23,320 --> 01:28:26,510
I mean, there just has
to be some boundaries, Viola.

1670
01:28:26,680 --> 01:28:28,010
I can do boundaries!

1671
01:28:29,520 --> 01:28:32,550
I don't love boundaries
but I can do them.

1672
01:28:32,730 --> 01:28:35,820
How about the number of times
