1673
01:28:35,990 --> 01:28:37,850
Can we limit that
to, like, one?

1674
01:28:38,030 --> 01:28:40,860
I need at least
four minimum.

1675
01:28:41,030 --> 01:28:43,020
- He's 35 years old.
- Three?

1676
01:28:43,200 --> 01:28:44,960
- Two.
- Deal.

1677
01:28:45,130 --> 01:28:47,890
Two long-ass calls!

1678
01:28:48,070 --> 01:28:49,890
When Kevin and I
have kids,

1679
01:28:50,060 --> 01:28:52,030
