- Will be solicited when needed.

1682
01:28:57,840 --> 01:29:00,500
All right, as long as one kid
is named after me.

1683
01:29:00,680 --> 01:29:03,300
- Middle name.
- Deal.

1684
01:29:03,470 --> 01:29:04,630
What else?

1685
01:29:04,810 --> 01:29:07,040
Holidays
and special occasions.

1686
01:29:07,210 --> 01:29:09,300
Are you gonna keep
me away?

1687
01:29:09,480 --> 01:29:13,470
You must be present
for every Christmas,

1688
01:29:13,640 --> 01:29:16,810
Thanksgiving,
birthday,

1689
01:29:16,980 --> 01:29:19,780
school play,
clarinet recital

1690
01:29:19,960 --> 01:29:23,320
and soccer game
in our kids' lives.

1691
01:29:24,420 --> 01:29:26,680
I want you to love them
and spoil them

1692
01:29:26,860 --> 01:29:29,190
and teach them things
that Kevin and I can't.

1693
01:29:30,290 --> 01:29:32,230
Like how to throw
a right hook for example.

1694
01:29:35,700 --> 01:29:37,390
I want you there, Viola.

1695
01:29:37,560 --> 01:29:40,620
I do, up front and center.

1696
01:29:42,370 --> 01:29:45,100
From this point
I will not negotiate.

1697
01:29:45,270 --> 01:29:48,860
Damn. That girl can give
a nice little speech.

1698
01:29:50,480 --> 01:29:52,000
Deal?

1699
01:29:55,150 --> 01:29:57,480
can they call me "Aunt Viola"
instead of "Grandma"?

1700
01:29:57,650 --> 01:30:00,310
Fine.

1701
01:30:10,060 --> 01:30:12,190
Come on, unzip me.

1702
01:30:12,360 --> 01:30:15,020
Viola, you don't
have to wear that dress, really.

1703
01:30:15,900 --> 01:30:17,990
Yes, I do. Really.

1704
01:30:22,500 --> 01:30:24,900
Go, Kevin and Charlie!

1705
01:30:30,940 --> 01:30:31,930
Yeah!

1706
01:30:47,660 --> 01:30:50,720
Mom!

1707
01:30:50,890 --> 01:30:52,760
Do you really think I would leave without
saying goodbye?

1708
01:30:55,070 --> 01:30:56,930
I love you, Mom.

1709
01:30:57,100 --> 01:30:59,500
- Thanks for everything.
- Go.

1710
01:31:00,600 --> 01:31:02,160
Bye, you guys!

1711
01:31:04,100 --> 01:31:06,830
Okay, everybody gather around
the back of the car!

1712
01:31:07,710 --> 01:31:09,470
Charlie!

1713
01:31:09,640 --> 01:31:11,930
Charlie, right here!
Right here, Charlie!

1714
01:31:30,830 --> 01:31:32,460
Sheesh.

1715
01:31:32,630 --> 01:31:35,970
- Hawaii! I cannot wait!
- I know. I can't either.

1716
01:31:37,970 --> 01:31:39,060
Have a great
time in Hawaii!

1717
01:31:39,240 --> 01:31:41,330
- Good luck!
- Have fun in Hawaii!

1718
01:31:45,540 --> 01:31:47,430
Just you and me
now, Ruby!

1719
01:31:47,610 --> 01:31:51,500
Jesus. Who did I kill
in a past life?

1720
01:31:51,670 --> 01:31:53,700
And take off
that damn dress.

1721
01:31:53,880 --> 01:31:55,170
You look like
a giant peach cobbler.

1722
01:31:55,340 --> 01:31:57,000
You're making me hungry.

1723
01:31:57,180 --> 01:32:00,310
Come on, weathergirl,
I'll buy you a box of wine.